BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-trip-008@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260918
SUMMARY:[Flight] Depart Zwijndrecht to Taipei via Amsterdam 11:00
DESCRIPTION:Departure day schedule:\n04:30 Wake up\n05:00 Final luggage check (passport / Entry Permit / tickets / EUR 300-500 cash / debit card / travel insurance)\n05:30 Train from Zwijndrecht to Rotterdam Centraal to Schiphol Airport (~1.5-2h with transfer)\n07:30 Arrive at Schiphol Airport\n07:30-08:30 Check-in / baggage drop / security\n09:00 Through security, head to gate\n11:00 Flight departs Amsterdam to Taipei\n\nTrain route: Zwijndrecht -> Rotterdam Centraal -> Schiphol.\nSleep early the night before! Check NS App for first train schedule (~05:00).
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT15H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Wake up at 04:30 tomorrow! Sleep early tonight! Departure from Zwijndrecht!
END:VALARM
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT1H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Wake up in 1 hour! 04:30 departure day!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-trip-009@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260923
SUMMARY:[Buy] Alishan Sunrise Train Ticket (Sep 24 early morning)
DESCRIPTION:Must buy today afternoon!\nTime: 1:00 PM - 4:00 PM (sales open at 1 PM, sells out fast!)\nLocation: Alishan Station\nArrive before 12:30 to queue!\nThis is the Zhushan Line train ticket for tomorrow sunrise viewing.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT1H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Go to Alishan Station in 1 hour to queue for sunrise train ticket!
END:VALARM
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:PT12H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Go to Alishan Station at 1 PM today to buy sunrise train ticket!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-trip-010@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260919
SUMMARY:[Arrive] Taipei 06:15
DESCRIPTION:Arrive Taoyuan Airport (TPE) at 06:15.\n\nToday's plan:\n1. Airport MRT to city\n2. Drop bags at hotel\n3. Buy EasyCard + SIM card + exchange TWD\n4. Rest to adjust to jet lag\n5. 3-4 PM: Elephant Mountain for Taipei 101 photo\n6. Evening: Ningxia Night Market
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-trip-011@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261004
SUMMARY:[Flight] Depart Kaohsiung to Nanjing 11:40
DESCRIPTION:Flight: Kaohsiung (KHH) to Nanjing.\nDepart: 11:40. Arrive: 14:00.\n\nReminders:\n- Kaohsiung Airport customs is fast, arrive 2-2.5 hours before\n- 09:00-09:30 leave hotel\n- This is Day 15 of Entry Permit (last legal day)! Must depart today!
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT4H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Flight in 4 hours! Kaohsiung to Nanjing 11:40. Last legal day of stay!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

