BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-food-001@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260912
SUMMARY:[Food] Book A-Hsia Restaurant Tainan (Sep 26 dinner)
DESCRIPTION:Michelin-recommended Taiwanese cuisine, very popular!\nDinner date: Sep 26.\nBooking: Download inline APP, book 1-2 weeks ahead.\nBook now - popular time slots fill up!\nAddress: Tainan, West Central Dist, Zhongyi Rd Sec 2 Lane 84 No 16.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-P3D
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Book A-Hsia Restaurant on inline APP if not done yet!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-food-002@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261002
SUMMARY:[Food] Book Re-chao Restaurant Kaohsiung (Oct 3 dinner)
DESCRIPTION:Last night Taiwanese stir-fry dinner! With Taiwan Beer.\nDinner date: Oct 3.\nRecommended: Hai-Bao Seafood / Sha-Ka-Dang.\nBooking: Call 1 day ahead (weekends get busy).\nCall today after arriving in Kaohsiung to book tomorrow night!
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:PT9H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Call to book Re-chao restaurant for tomorrow night after arriving in Kaohsiung!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-food-003@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260919
SUMMARY:[Arrive] Buy EasyCard + SIM card + Exchange TWD at airport
DESCRIPTION:First things to do after arriving at Taoyuan Airport:\n1. Exchange TWD: Terminal 2 Floor 1 Bank of Taiwan / Mega Bank (bring EUR 300-500)\n2. Chunghwa Telecom SIM card: need passport, ~10 min, NT$300-500 unlimited data\n3. Buy EasyCard: airport convenience store (deposit NT$100) + top up NT$1000\n\nAll three can be done inside the airport terminal!
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:PT0S
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Arrived in Taiwan! Exchange currency + get SIM card + buy EasyCard!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-food-004@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260920
SUMMARY:[Food] Fu Hang Soy Milk - arrive before 7:30 AM!
DESCRIPTION:Taipei's most famous breakfast spot!\nArrive before 7:30 AM to avoid 30-60 min queue.\nLocation: Near Shandao Temple Station, Zhongxiao E Rd Sec 1 No 108.\nMust order: thick flatbread with egg, salty soy milk.\nQueue is serious even on weekdays!
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT13H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Go to Fu Hang Soy Milk at 7:30 AM tomorrow! Sleep early tonight!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-food-005@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260926
SUMMARY:[Food] Tainan queue restaurants today!
DESCRIPTION:Tainan food day - two famous queue spots:\n\n1. A-Tang Savory Porridge: opens 06:00, queue 1hr+. Go early!\n   Address: Tainan, West Central Dist, Ximen Rd Sec 1 No 728.\n\n2. Liu-Qian Beef Soup (optional): opens 05:00! Limited quantity.\n   Address: Tainan, West Central Dist, Haian Rd Sec 1 No 63.\n\nA-Hsia Restaurant tonight (already booked via inline APP).
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT13H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Wake up early tomorrow! A-Tang opens at 6 AM / Liu-Qian at 5 AM!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-food-006@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260924
SUMMARY:[Food] Alishan sunrise ticket + confirm rafting booking
DESCRIPTION:Today at Alishan:\nGo to Alishan Station before 1 PM to queue for tomorrow's sunrise train ticket! (Already in transport reminders)\n\nAlso confirm: Xiuguluan River Rafting (Sep 30) is booked on Klook/KKday?\nIf not booked yet, book today!
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:PT8H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Buy sunrise train ticket at 1 PM today! Also confirm rafting booking!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-food-007@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260925
SUMMARY:[Food] Chiayi Turkey Rice for lunch!
DESCRIPTION:On the way down from Alishan to Tainan, must stop in Chiayi for turkey rice!\n\nRecommended: any local shop near Chiayi Station.\nOr Lin-Cong-Ming sand-pot fish head nearby.\n\nThis is the first hot meal after descending - super satisfying!
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:PT6H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Stop in Chiayi for turkey rice today on the way down!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260625T000000Z
UID:tw-food-008@taiwan-itinerary
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260928
SUMMARY:[Food] Houpihu Seafood for lunch in Kenting!
DESCRIPTION:Today in Kenting, lunch at Houpihu seafood!\n\nRecommended: A-Xing Sashimi.\nBest value seafood in Taiwan! Sashimi from NT$100.\nMonday = fewer people, shorter queue.\nAddress: Pingtung, Hengchun, Daguang Rd No 79-30.
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:PT7H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Lunch at Houpihu seafood today! A-Xing Sashimi!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

